{"type":"message","id":"ecf7a311","parentId":"c6cc8590","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:54:01.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself. The session list shows only the cron session's own message, not an active user conversation. The session was updated at 1775066029646 which is... let me calculate. That's a timestamp in milliseconds. Let me check if it's within the last 5 minutes.\n\nCurrent time: 2026-04-02T01:53:00+08:00 = 2026-04-01T17:53:00 UTC = 1775065980000 ms approximately.\n\n1775066029646 - 1775065980000 = ~49646ms ≈ 49 seconds ago.\n\nThe session shown is the cron session itself, not a user conversation. \n\nSince there are no other sessions besides the cron session executing right now, there's no active user conversation happening, so I should proceed with the self-learning task. Now I need to search for the latest developments in enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services to gather insights for Dao Jian Network.","thinkingSignature":"da4ffea01a35772f6fb05df2c32dad7c533cc83517ae4ddc555150d0a2b6a5bf"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前 cron 会话本身，没有活跃的用户对话。开始执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_267hu7v6n8an_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":809,"output":275,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45065,"cost":{"input":0.0002427,"output":0.00033,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00189213}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775066033896}}
{"type":"message","id":"f582a940","parentId":"ecf7a311","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:54:01.184Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_267hu7v6n8an_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775066041180}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b8e5f2b","parentId":"f582a940","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:54:03.477Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check for available skills to use for web search.","thinkingSignature":"5486decd797fd0323e91dedde42cd47589db9c5f7ebe214bd61cddd12dd7508e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_42trrl0hbhmm_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1151,"output":56,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45188,"cost":{"input":0.0003453,"output":0.0000672,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00173193}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775066041183}}
{"type":"message","id":"8126de0b","parentId":"0b8e5f2b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:54:03.483Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_42trrl0hbhmm_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775066043480}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c95b556","parentId":"8126de0b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:54:07.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest industry trends related to Dao Jian Network's business areas.","thinkingSignature":"7c9bb2396f2d11b0190a822a8128ca10708c78119c1d2dd8f79680ba9b2a020c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hqialsae0mbw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新趋势政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hqialsae0mbw_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026 最新动态技术趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hqialsae0mbw_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 市场动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1722,"output":180,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45883,"cost":{"input":0.0005166,"output":0.000216,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00205203}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775066043483}}
